channel.title: 317 PI Fixing lime green trees
channel.description: I've got tom's cache suite, and it opens my cache with no errors, but I looked in all the sections and i found one that was 1570 and opened up the tree's object in the frame, i deleted it and my client won't start. I'll undo it, but can anyone give me a detailed tut?

item.title: 317 PI Fixing lime green trees
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Dude it’s literally just replacing the 1570.dat with the old tree model.

Most of the clients came with a 1570.old.dat
Rename it to 1570.dat and then replace the one in your cache. done.

Read full topic
